--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages createrepo.

This utility will generate a common metadata repository from a directory of rpm
packages.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: createrepo
       createrepo_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: createrepo
       createrepo_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  createrepo_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PACKAGES
  createrepo
    Version: >= 0.9
    Name   :
      RedHat 6: 'createrepo'
      CentOS 6: 'createrepo'

